Pre-Game Insights: Madagascar and Gambia will be looking to secure their first win in Group A of the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers.
Both teams have struggled in their last qualifying matches, with Madagascar failing to win in their last 12 games and Gambia also struggling with nine losses in their last outings.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is significant for both teams as they aim to end their dry spells in qualifying matches.
